{"tid":963474,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港「希望指數」急插　全球第五悲觀","createTime":"2018-12-31T15:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T15:51:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1d47302a1088a3f7aac992acb033981ffe2a2c09","tid":963474,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:02:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181231/20580481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F20580481&d=6yZlErWEhdfD04ocpivlSgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=245eb888\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F20580481&h=7f2e026e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181231/20580481</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月31日 <br />\n<br />\n港「希望指數」急插　全球第五悲觀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181231/large/16735805.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181231%2Flarge%2F16735805.jpg&h=4941bed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人對前景越來越悲觀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】2018年轉眼將逝，對於明年會否更好，港人卻不抱希望。據國際民意調查機構「蓋洛普（Gallup）」最新年度報告，香港的「希望指數（Hope Index）」按年急挫35分，由去年+10分直插至-25分，頓成全球最悲觀地區第五位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181231/large/a0204a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181231%2Flarge%2Fa0204a.gif&h=d68475ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最憂心明年世界不和平<br />\n<br />\n中大社會工作學系副教授黃洪認為包括政治上佔中九子審訊、「明日大嶼」及沙中綫醜聞，以至經濟不景氣等，令港人對政府感不滿，未來「大家覺得好難去控制周圍嘅環境，或自己嘅命運」，故悲觀情緒應運而生。<br />\n<br />\n「你認為2019年會比2018年更好、更差或是不分上下？」國際民意調查機構「蓋洛普」綜合全球51個國家或地區近月的民意調查，分析出五大地區對明年最感悲觀，首兩名都是毗鄰戰火中的中東國家約旦（-48分）和黎巴嫩（-42分），其次為連續兩年登榜的意大利（-40分），南韓（-30分）緊隨其後；惟土地面積及人口都遠不及前四者的香港（-25分），今年榜上有名，成第五大最悲觀地區；同時更成為全球最憂心明年將不再世界和平的第二位。<br />\n<br />\n調查並無針對政治、經濟或社會哪一層面，該調查機構主席Kancho Stoychev指，數據反映越富有國家或地區、越對來年不抱期望，「相比無法擁有，人們更怕失去已擁有的事物」。黃洪指，「希望指數」按年急跌變負數，並非由單一事件引致，反是由連串事件構成的趨勢，更令人難以對來年抱有希望。<br />\n<br />\n身兼中大亞太研究所生活質素研究中心主任的黃洪舉例指，佔中九子和填海造地等事件，市民都難以理解政府處事手段；加上中美貿易戰使環球經濟不景氣，樓市、股市紛紛下挫致人心惶惶，悲觀情緒或已成趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n香港的「希望指數」是根據本地研究機構每年11月訪問約500人數據整合所得，去年全球平均分為+17分，與香港得分相若；惟平均分今年微跌2分。翻查資料，中大年中公佈的香港生活質素指數亦反映，言論自由指數的評分自2014年傘運後按年下跌，去年整體指數亦較2016年微跌。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄧溢禧  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n冒寒排隊攞飛　長者轟安排差<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日提醒你：東海堂雪糕買一送一"},{"pid":"18bdbec903699dc657902bdee2e449526fdb89bb","tid":963474,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"真係好悲"},{"pid":"658e5429a667b87d23584cb37f7f54e3b7c1db17","tid":963474,"uid":60049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"悲過敘利亞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757d92713d347e6efebdcd470a99bbcd60031f68","tid":963474,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"658e5429a667b87d23584cb37f7f54e3b7c1db17","tid":963474,"uid":60049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"悲過敘利亞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4884caf37e711e6fd3fbd3c7249f77aff1549c7c","tid":963474,"uid":59501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"多謝支那又送大禮<br />\n超英趕美<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9749b73ea478601eefd25690237550b9033febb","tid":963474,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:33:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2a03a36b2ffb552d3e7d77fa0ed699482fbc401","tid":963474,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"658e5429a667b87d23584cb37f7f54e3b7c1db17","tid":963474,"uid":60049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"悲過敘利亞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:38:25.000Z","msg":"仲有贏勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2fd5615ef911cfd37dd6b63a5be7f08b823188","tid":963474,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"點會呀 ，點止-25分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}